import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import "./style.css"; export default function SideBar(props) { useEffect(() => { $('#catmenu li.active').addClass('open').children('ul').show(); $('#catmenu li.has-sub>a').on('click', function () { $(this).removeAttr('href'); var element = $(this).parent('li'); if (element.hasClass('open')) { element.removeClass('open'); element.find('li').removeClass('open'); element.find('ul').slideUp(200); } else { element.addClass('open'); element.children('ul').slideDown(200); element.siblings('li').children('ul').slideUp(200); element.siblings('li').removeClass('open'); element.siblings('li').find('li').removeClass('open'); element.siblings('li').find('ul').slideUp(200); } }); }) return (
